-- Maps a job (the framework job string) to the regions it should receive
-- dispatch alerts for. Use the `region` strings from Config.Towns/Districts
-- above. A job not listed here gets ALL alerts (legacy behavior). An empty
-- list `{}` means "no alerts at all" — useful to mute a job temporarily.
